Argued February 1, affirmed February 1, 1973 STATE OF OREGON, Respondent, v. ALBERT RUSSELL ZANDER (No. 1112), Appellant. 505 P2d 358 Charles R. Cater, La Grande, argued the cause and filed the brief for appellant. Jesse R. Himmelsbach, Jr., District Attorney, Baker, appeared for respondent.

Before Schwab, Chief Judge, and Langtry and Fort, Judges.
